						 <p>I don't know what kind of summoning circle you had to set up to make this, but the product of your hubris was my intense enjoyment. It read so well I forgot I was reading a skip. The concept is so silly but the pacing of presentation was perfect to keep the silliness at bay (similarly, it would have been so, so easy to make this a GaW thing, which would have killed it). So yeah. Fortnite meme death god. +1. Somehow.</p> 
