					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like this to start with because it starts serious then successfully shifts into humour, I like it doubly because it takes the silly meme humour and pop culture references one might expect from older -J articles and transposes it into a serious mainlister in a way that actually works, and triply because it references one of my least favorite pieces of pop culture from this decade and I still enjoy the article.</p> <blockquote> <p>See attached documentation for GOI-3824 (“Games Workshop”)</p> </blockquote> <p>But even if none of that were true this on its own earns a hearty +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
